content.rendered: Designed to easily compact materials like gravel, soil, and asphalt, the 60 inch diesel dual drum ride-on roller is a perfect tool for any small to medium sized paving jobs. Its 60 inch vibratory drums along with its small build make it easy to steer, which prevents overlap and improves maneuverability.
